## 🚀 Installation Steps

### 1. Install Dependencies
```bash
pip install semantic-kernel --break-system-packages
```

### 2. File Structure
```
your_project/
├── agents/
│   └── host_agent/
│       ├── entry.py              # ✏️ Updated
│       ├── orchestrator.py       # 🔥 Refactored
│       ├── sk_planner.py         # ✨ NEW
│       ├── sk_plugins.py         # ✨ NEW
│       ├── agent_connect.py      # ✅ No change
│       └── query_router.py       # ❌ DELETE THIS
```

### 3. Copy Files to Your Project

**Copy these NEW files:**
```bash
# Copy sk_planner.py to your project
cp sk_planner.py agents/host_agent/

# Copy sk_plugins.py to your project
cp sk_plugins.py agents/host_agent/

# Copy updated orchestrator.py
cp orchestrator.py agents/host_agent/

# Copy updated entry.py
cp entry.py agents/host_agent/
```

**Delete old file:**
```bash
rm agents/host_agent/query_router.py
```

### 4. Verify .env Configuration
Make sure your `.env` has Azure OpenAI credentials:
```bash
AZURE_OPENAI_API_KEY=your_key_here
AZURE_OPENAI_ENDPOINT=https://your-resource.openai.azure.com/
AZURE_OPENAI_DEPLOYMENT=your_deployment_name
AZURE_OPENAI_API_VERSION=2024-02-15-preview
```

